React Components

What is Component?
--- Piece of code/ block code /file for specific task.
What is React Component?

--
1) Class Components
   -- class keywords and extends React.Components
   -- it has one method is requied, is render() { }
   -- In render() {} - it should return one element(JSX elements) 
   -- If want avialable to other places, we need to exports
      -- export default <ComponentName>

2) Function Components  -- 16.8 v completely its React Hooks
   --- function <funcitonName>
   -- it should return one element ie JSX element

Note: While creating a class Component or Function Component we need to naming rules.
      --  PascalCase <CardData>
      -- PascalCase is a naming convention in which the first letter of each word in a compound word is capitalized

------------------------------------------------------------------------

Styling(applying CSS/ cascading/rending the styles to React JS elements)

How to apply the Styling?

1) Class Component
   CSS styles : 1) inline 2) internal 3) external CSS

   Note: We are applying styles to JSX element, not HTML.
   class - className
   <br>  - <br/>
           <Form/>
   styles
   background-color  - backgroundColor 

2) Function Component
   CSS styles : 1) inline 2) internal 3) external CSS